headline: DAT to showcase new services at the Walcott Truckers Jamboree
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., July 10, 2025--DAT Freight & Analytics will present its new Outgo freight factoring services and expanded DAT One capabilities next month at the Walcott Truckers Jamboree, a three-day celebration of trucking and the people who keep the industry rolling.
